name: Thomas Wolfe
body:
## Hi,
I'm Thomas, a recent graduate from the University of Illinois at Urbana-
Champaign (UIUC). While at UIUC I studied Statistics and during my Senior year
I started taking CS classes. After my first CS class I got hooked on
programming and instead of going back to school to finish up a CS degree I am
attending a coding bootcamp in Silicon Valley (Coding House). When I'm not
coding you will most likely find me doing one of the following:
reading, working on my latest startup idea, playing with my dog, analyzing
data, eating, running,practicing guitar, taking a walk outside, or re-watching
episodes of The Office for about the 10th time.
